THEMED TEAM-UP: HERALD: If Terrax is on a Herald themed team, Terrax has "POWER: KO all opposing bystanders within range and line of fire."
Special Powers
MOVEMENT: This character can move through Blocking terrain. Immediately after movement resolves, destroy all Blocking terrain moved through.
THE EARTH SHIFTS AND HEAVES AND BOWS TO HIS POWERFUL COMMAND!: Quake, Giant Reach: 3. When Terrax uses Quake, after resolutions generate a blocking terrain marker adjacent to each hit character. At the beginning of your next turn, remove all blocking terrain markers generated this way.
TERRAX SHALL DESTROY YOU!: STOP. Invulnerability, Regeneration.
